{"tid":366110,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有啲野講緣份嘅","createTime":"2017-08-19T18:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T03:56:48.000Z","uid":69599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"067d37448a931488f4bb433887c107e25436bcd6","tid":366110,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:03:53.000Z","msg":"有時你溝到人，人地未必好愛你㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n眼見好多情侶都因為各大小事而吵架，鬧分手，<br />\n<br />\n當中必有原因，有時候我地會好執著去證明對方錯，<br />\n<br />\n但其實一段關係真係有對錯之分咩？<br />\n<br />\n只要我地明白人夾人，合則來不合則去，其實好多事都沒有對錯之分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打個比喻: 女方想落club ，男方唔比，其實雙方都<br />\n冇錯，只係你想要的不是我，我想要的亦不是你。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣大家都會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1999請建諒 借朋友ac開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cd32aa8a0976512727019e6490426458beaef1","tid":366110,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:05:15.000Z","msg":"見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaf84fc8b65e91a0005d2246a8306993beb5a10","tid":366110,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"如果條女派帽<br />\n仲應唔應該分對錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你個名一樣 百事有可樂"},{"pid":"5704e0efb53e2814f5c8a39395ef054031350c01","tid":366110,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果條女派帽<br />\n仲應唔應該分對錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你個名一樣 百事有可樂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留意我只係講好多事 並非全部，當然女方應該處理<br />\n<br />\n得更好，要揾第二個都應該等分手左之後，否則的<br />\n<br />\n確冇尊重過你地嘅關係。"},{"pid":"88f3c437a3a0763f2ce6c7d2953a203a7c4582f2","tid":366110,"uid":89331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"講就易　到分手個陣點都會hurt"},{"pid":"41eab9376e3dca05f45eb25538f5a3ac4d63b720","tid":366110,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講就易　到分手個陣點都會hurt</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大丈夫何患無妻？"},{"pid":"f945889765db4d094a752023989e829855a54443","tid":366110,"uid":72266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T23:25:32.000Z","msg":"[i][/⼁<blockquote><strong>引用</strong></blockquote>[img]圖片網址 [/img]<del></del>也<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"54f8e9dbb632d04eaeb21610910d51bd2d8f166c","tid":366110,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T23:28:47.000Z","msg":"只係大家比幾多心機落一段感情<br />\n但唔應該計較邊個付出多d"},{"pid":"370dafe4742ffacb95cfedc593a354fa04c26250","tid":366110,"uid":136681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"有緣無份呢 時間唔啱？<br />\n我只係佢其一 <br />\n佢係我唯一啊屌"}]}